## Basic RAG Architecture

```text
User Query
     ↓
Embedding Model
     ↓
Vector Search
     ↓
Relevant Context Retrieved
     ↓
LLM + Context
     ↓
Generated Response
```

---

## Conclusion

RAG enhances Large Language Models by giving them access to external knowledge sources. It is one of the most important architectures used in modern AI applications for building reliable and context-aware systems.
